HEADWORD: chiropractic
<hw>chiropractic</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a method of medical treatment
that manipulates body structures, especially the spine, in the belief
that it restores proper nerve functioning.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

